{% schema %}
  {
    
    "name": "Section 3",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-607384197513872282 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/sheikhashadul/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_ARTICLE&editorId=607381796862034487&sectionId=607384197513872282)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1KQWhMyxG_text","label":"gg1KQWhMyxG_text","default":"<p>And the truth is, the beauty industry would prefer it if you never found out about this Progerin-reducing tweak because once you see the results for yourself, the days of you buying cream after cream will be well and truly over.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3qqTazfO2_text","label":"gg3qqTazfO2_text","default":"That's Why I Made This Breakthrough Skincare Report."},{"type":"html","id":"gg2Rc6G8LXc_text","label":"gg2Rc6G8LXc_text","default":"<p>My name is</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCvmVWuFoM_text","label":"ggCvmVWuFoM_text","default":"<p>Dr. Manjula Jegasothy</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRfvt8DGjf_text","label":"ggRfvt8DGjf_text","default":"<p>and I'm a leading dermatologist from Korea, Florida.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggABItSTyUA_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggABItSTyUA_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s2bx2hdimg.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-BEfuqHLw_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg-BEfuqHLw_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/dermatologist-profile_08c5fe82-ed35-462b-b49b-d9878bbcc811.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-BEfuqHLw_srcSet_mobile_src","label":"gg-BEfuqHLw_srcSet_mobile_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Generated_Image_February_20_2026_-_11_38PM_copy_9926b4b9-3656-4301-a244-14f6efc2d053.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOOMltb1SK_text","label":"ggOOMltb1SK_text","default":"<p>As founder of the world-renowned<br>Korea Skin Institute and a regular speaker at the Cosmetic Surgery Forum &amp; Florida Society of Dermatologic Surgeons, I've spent the last 20 years helping women defy their years.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3gLhL9HDC_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg3gLhL9HDC_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Generated_Image_February_20_2026_-_11_38PM_copy_9926b4b9-3656-4301-a244-14f6efc2d053.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7XgSzov0F_text","label":"gg7XgSzov0F_text","default":"<p>Despite being Korea's most sought-after dermatologist, treating A-list celebrities, and having access to every cutting-edge treatment, I was heartbroken watching women like Beverly, one of my long-time patients, struggle with premature aging.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTKOvQiepL_text","label":"ggTKOvQiepL_text","default":"<p>At just 55, her face showed deep lines, sagging jowls, and a loss of firmness that made her look 15 years older than her actual age. She had tried everything -- from $500 creams to painful and risky procedures.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzadrGizPU_text","label":"ggzadrGizPU_text","default":"<p>\"Every morning I'd look in the mirror and barely recognize myself,\" Beverly told me. \"I felt like I was disappearing, watching my youthful appearance slip away despite doing everything right.\"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYKI5tqYft_text","label":"ggYKI5tqYft_text","default":"<p>That was then.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6MUVPTXNA_text","label":"gg6MUVPTXNA_text","default":"<p><strong>Today, I'm proud to say that not only does Beverly look 15 years younger, she's actually glowing with confidence because her skin finally looks as young as she feels.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUZjIpONfG_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggUZjIpONfG_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s2arw.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9Svp9nc1I_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg9Svp9nc1I_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s2img_29938c96-fa30-4841-a7de-cddf1b7ad193.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9Svp9nc1I_srcSet_tablet_src","label":"gg9Svp9nc1I_srcSet_tablet_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s2img_29938c96-fa30-4841-a7de-cddf1b7ad193.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggh4nPDO9YS_text","label":"ggh4nPDO9YS_text","default":"<p>Best of all, I've now helped thousands of women achieve the same results... including women of EVERY age, many of whom had given up hope of ever looking youthful again.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggc8pbmE8CN_text","label":"ggc8pbmE8CN_text","default":"<p>To achieve this type of skin transformation yourself...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWTDgrNLap_childItem_0","label":"ggWTDgrNLap_childItem_0","default":"<p>You do <u>not </u>need invasive surgery.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWTDgrNLap_childItem_1","label":"ggWTDgrNLap_childItem_1","default":"<p>You do <u>not </u>need painful injections.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWTDgrNLap_childItem_2","label":"ggWTDgrNLap_childItem_2","default":"<p>You do <u>not </u>need expensive laser treatments.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWTDgrNLap_childItem_3","label":"ggWTDgrNLap_childItem_3","default":"<p>And you don&#039;t need $500 creams...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbThhKUQwM_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggbThhKUQwM_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s2bx3img.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggyZsT5Jfxu_text","label":"ggyZsT5Jfxu_text","default":"<p>What you <strong>DO </strong>need is to understand one – just one – crucial discovery about aging skin, and if you do, I can practically guarantee your appearance will transform in a matter of weeks.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQXUpT8YpJ_text","label":"ggQXUpT8YpJ_text","default":"<p>What's the one thing you need to understand?</p>"}],
